Version: 3.1.0

1. Open an extension point schema
2. Double click on an element on the definition page to open the properties view
3. double click Start editing a value in the property page
4. Close the editor by pressing the 'x'
5. Observe: a dialog should be displayed indicating there was a problem

A similar error can be observed when closing the property page while editing a
value.
